Package cz.cuni.mff.java.klima.pacman

Contains all used packages and classes necessary to run HungryPacMan game.

Classes are sorted into packages, each sub-package represents a logical part of the game.

This is the main package of the game and contains the GameLauncher class responsible for launching the game window, the Game class containing the main game loop and the Handler class used for handling game objects from within other classes.

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Game
    The Game class is the main class of the HungryPacMan game responsible for running the game loop (tick and render).
    GameLauncher
    The GameLauncher class contains the main method of the Hungry PacMan game.
    Handler
    The Handler class enables different game objects and entities to access each other when necessary.
